import React from 'react' import { useHistory } from 'react-router' function CountriesItem(props) { const { country } = props const history = useHistory return (
history.push(`/details/${country.name}`)}>

{country.name}

Population: {country.population}

Region: {country.region}

Capital: {country.capital}

) } export default CountriesItem
